<!DOCTYPE html><html> <head>  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initialscale=1.0" />  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />  <style type="text/css">@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {slot[style] {margin-right: 0 !important;}.columnDiv {margin-right: 0 !important;}}@media screen and (min-width: 480px) {slot[style] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}.columnDiv {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}}</style>  <style type="text/css">@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {.contentbuilderBaseColumnRow .columnCell {display:inline-block;width:100%}}</style>  <style type="text/css">.contentpageDefaultEmailTemplatePageTemplate .contentRoot {width: 600px;}@media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {.contentpageDefaultEmailTemplatePageTemplate .contentRoot {width: 320px;}}</style> </head> <body>  <table class="contentpageDefaultEmailTemplatePageTemplate" style="background-color: #E9EAEC;" role="presentation" id="contentpage_emailTemplateBodyContent" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">       <tr>     <td width="100%" align="center">      <table class="contentRoot" style="background-color: #FFFFFF;" role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">               <tr>         <td style="padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">          <table class="contentbuilderBaseColumnRow" style="align-items: flex-start; width: 100%; background-color:;" role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">                       <tr valign="top">             <td width="100%" class="columnCell" style="vertical-align: top;display: inline-block; float:left">              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; word-break:break-word;">                               <tr>                 <td>                  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; word-break: break-word; font-size: 14px" id="contentRegion" role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" locked="0">                                       <tr>                     <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:18px;"><strong>Dear Client,</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Unit -</strong></span><span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>&nbsp;{{{Opportunity.Customer_Unit_Name__c}}}</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>{{{Recipient.Broker_Address__c}}}</strong></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:16px;">Sale and Purchase Agreement (“SPA”)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; اتفاقية البيع والشراء</span><br /><br /> This notification is served to you in furtherance of the Sale and Purchase Agreement signed between you and Zoya One Real Estate Developments LLC for Off-Plan/Completed unit in our project Pristine by Zoya.<br /><br /> يتم تقديم هذه الإشعارات إليكم تنفيذاً لاتفاقية البيع والشراء الموقعة بين الشركة&nbsp;Zoya One Real Estate Developments LLC&nbsp; للوحدات قيد الإنشاء/المكتملة في مشروعنا&nbsp;Pristine by Zoya.<br /><br /><br /> Please note that you are at default in payment as per the payment schedule in the Sale and Purchase Agreement. According to the Schedule, payment of amount&nbsp; is overdue since . We request you to proceed with the payment of overdue amount within 15 days of service of this notice. We would like to bring to your attention that a penalty of AED 3,000 will be charged for the overdue installment(s) as per SPA clause.<br /><br /><span style="color:#e74c3c;"><strong>NOTE: The non-compliance to the payment may lead to attraction of penalties and/or termination procedure.</strong></span><br /><br /> يرجى العلم بأنك متخلف عن السداد وفقًا لجدول الدفعات الوارد في اتفاقية البيع والشراء.وبحسب الجدول، فإن مبلغ xxxx.xx مستحق الدفع منذ تاريخ .<br /> نرجو منكم<br /> المضي قدماً في سداد المبلغ المتأخر خلال 15 يوماً من تاريخ استلام هذا الإشعار.<br /><br /> نود أن نلفت انتباهكم إلى أنه سيتم فرض غرامة قدرها 3000 درهم إماراتي على الأقساط المتأخرة وفقًا لبند اتفاقية البيع والشراء.<br /> &nbsp;                       <div style="text-align: right;">                       <span style="color:#c0392b;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>ملاحظة: قد يؤدي عدم الالتزام بالدفع إلى فرض غرامات و/أو إجراءات إنهاء الخدمة.</strong></span>                      </div><br /> You are, hereby, requested to comply with the terms of the notification at the earliest.<br /><br /><strong><span style="font-size:16px;">If the payment has already been made, please disregard this email</span></strong><br /><br /> Yours sincerely,<br /> Authorized Signatory<br /> &nbsp;                       <div style="text-align: right;">                       يرجى منكم، بموجب هذا، الامتثال لشروط الإخطار في أقرب وقت ممكن. <br /><br /> مع خالص التحيات، <br /> المفوض بالتوقيع                      </div>                      <div>                       <br /> **If the payment has been made already, please send the evidence at the following email address and apologies for the inconvenience                      </div></td>                    </tr>                                     </table></td>                </tr>                             </table></td>            </tr>                     </table></td>        </tr>             </table></td>    </tr>     </table> </body></html>